NAME: Bed
DESCRIPTION__C: A bed is a piece of furniture which is used as a place to sleep or relax.

NAME: Cot
DESCRIPTION__C: A cot is an infant bed.

NAME: Bunk Bed
DESCRIPTION__C: A bunk bed is a type of bed in which one bed frame is stacked on top of another.

NAME: Chair
DESCRIPTION__C: A chair is a piece of furniture with a raised surface, commonly used to seat a single person.

NAME: School Desk
DESCRIPTION__C: A school desk is a piece of furniture with a flat table-style work surface used in a school.

NAME: Tinker Cube
DESCRIPTION__C: A sample object created in Tinkercad

NAME: Wind Turbine
DESCRIPTION__C: A wind turbine is a device that converts the wind's energy into electrical power.

NAME: Antenna
DESCRIPTION__C: Allows to receive phone, TV, radio and Internet signal.

NAME: Solar Panel
DESCRIPTION__C: Solar panel refers to a panel designed to absorb the sun's rays as a source of energy for generating electricity or heating.

NAME: Double Bed
DESCRIPTION__C: A large bed for two persons.
